# Ipv4-Addressing-and-Subnetting

## What This Is
Addressing and Subnetting is the first small step on this big journey.
It is important in a sense that, without this key foundational knowledge your exam learning will be
way more difficult especailly if we start discussing Azure-related services that involves subnetting.
Subnetting is the skill and art of allocating the right amount of network resources for what you need.
Addressing helps you understand why ip addresses are that way, certain kinds of ip addresses and protocols.

## What I Built
I made a full-fledged guide on those aforementioned topics, to promote full
understanding of subnetting. It's extremely beginner-friendly and uses the Feynman
approach to the fullest while also considering flow and efficiency.

